{
  "stem": "22979.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So, you know, when you saw so many years the same [NON-ENGLISH]-- in 1943, was already the SS, you know, in-- in the-- our commando.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Otto Graff too.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Then Gottfried Weiser who I was witness-- a witness in [INAUDIBLE] was there too!",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we-- you know, and I have such a good memory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I saw him, and I remembered him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I remember everything what happened 55 years ago, but I hardly can remember what happened yesterday what I had for lunch.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You'd ?] remember?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I don't, unless it was something good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway-- so that's the reason, you know, I go and I'm a witness because I promised myself-- first of all, I wanted to live.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I wanted at least to point at one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I feel so lucky and proud that I could at least one bring to justice.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was really something what I-- what I earned and I wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I wanted to live just for this reason.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so what can I say?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I will have to tell you now what happened when the Hungarian came.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The first transport from Hungary came the 15th of May, 1944.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were already in this special assigned camp where you know, their belongings were stored.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's, you know, you have no idea.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In front of us, to the entrance, to the gas chambers, and to the crematorias were lines day and night.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The crematoria 4-- 1 2 on one side, the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Other side where we were working, the other two.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Lined up-- it was hot in this last summer of 1944 when I was still there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the crowds and the heat and the lines, endless.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Endless.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, you couldn't see the last end.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
